            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="913.949" end="x">Well, and . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Janis B.</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bJanis" start="940.097" end="x">But, but . . .</span>
