                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="961.647" end="x">[Did they start?] to arrest many people?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Janis B.</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bJanis" start="963.334" end="x">Not from our establishment—</span>
