            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="966.990" end="x">[<i>interrupts</i>] No, I am thinking [about Jews?].</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Janis B.</span>:
