            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Janis B.</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bJanis" start="1352.019" end="x">Then they put us on a train again and . . . and [again?] they took me and nearly 30 people to <a class="placename" href="#vothL130">Hamburg</a>.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1364.669" end="x">So.</span>
        </li>
