            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Janis B.</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bJanis" start="1385.706" end="x">Yes. [In the outskirts?] of <a class="placename" href="#vothL130">Hamburg</a>—</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1388.081" end="x">[<i>interrupting each other</i>] Did you work there in a factory?</span>
